com.tsgrp.migration.util

Class RosettaCSV

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tsgrp.migration.util.RosettaExcel
      • com.tsgrp.migration.util.RosettaCSV
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Rosetta

    public class RosettaCSV
extends RosettaExcel
    Rosetta class which translates strings stored in an CSV file. Properly formatted files should contain the old strings in the 1st column and the corresponding new strings in the 2nd column. Optional header rows can be included but the number of rows must be injected to ensure proper translation.
